      "factId": "hz.web.fb2f7e5988edb9ea.fact.2",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "Flywheel\\u2019s cloud-based platform offers blazing-fast speeds, top-notch security, and a reimagined SFTP.\",\"page_faq\":\"yes\",\"faq\":[{\"faq_question\":\"What does managed hosting mean?\",\"faq_answer\":\"<p>As a managed hosting platform for WordPress, Flywheel is going to take care of a bunch of the technical nitty-gritty stuff, so you can get back to doing what you love and growing your business.<\\/p>\\n<p>Here are the main <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/getflywheel.com\\/layout\\/managed-wordpress-hosting-benefits\\/\\\">benefits of a true managed hosting platform for WordPress<\\/a>\\u00a0like Flywheel:<\\/p>\\n<p><strong>Managed caching and performance:<\\/strong> We handle caching for you at the server level, using super fast servers to begin with, and even work individually with our customers to further optimize their sites for the best performance.",
